## Ignore Visual Studio Code files
.vscode/**
.vscode-test/**

## Ignore build files
*.vsix
node_modules/**
out/**
dist/**

## Ignore development files
.eslintrc.json
.gitignore
tsconfig.json
webpack.config.js
.env
.env.example

## Ignore documentation sources (mantém README, CHANGELOG e docs/functions usados em runtime)
*.md
!README.md
!CHANGELOG.md
docs/*.md
docs/prompts/**
!docs/functions/**

## Ignore test files
test/**
*.test.js
*.spec.js

## Ignore CI/CD files
.github/**
.gitlab-ci.yml
azure-pipelines.yml

## Ignore editor files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/**
*.swp
*.swo

## Ignore development sources (não necessários em runtime)
.claude/**
scripts/**
data/**
Exemplos de Arquivos/**
Formata*/**

## Keep only necessary files for extension
!package.json
!language-configuration.json
!syntaxes/**
!snippets/**
!images/**
!LICENSE
